Season 6 (2010) - 22 Episodes

Season six of Supernatural, an American paranormal drama television series created by Eric Kripke, premiered September 24, 2010, and concluded May 20, 2011, airing 22 episodes. The season begins a year after the happenings of the previous season finale with Dean Winchester living a happy and normal life. Mysteriously, Sam Winchester freed from Lucifer's cage in Hell and teams up with Dean, who leaves his new life behind and becomes a hunter again. In the United States the season aired on Fridays at 9:00 P.M. ET on the CW television network
